$ R: tidyverse packages

*tidyverse* is an ecosystem of packages that were designed with a common API and a shared philosophy:
  • → development/languages/R/packages/ggplot2[ggplot2]
  • → development/languages/R/packages/dplyr[dplyr]
  • → development/languages/R/packages/tidyr[tidyr]
  • → development/languages/R/packages/rlang[rlang]
  • … ?

{ Tibble #tidyverse-tibble

  Tibbles are → development/languages/R/data-structures/data-frame[data frames] that are tweaked to work better in the tidyverse.

}

